      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is currently in running order, making it a suitable option for someone looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic commuter. While it starts and drives, it shows significant signs of age, including some noticeable exterior scratches and interior wear on the upholstery. There are a few minor mechanical items that will likely require maintenance in the near future, such as aging tires and a noisy exhaust. It\u2019s a solid foundation for someone willing to put in a little work.",
