      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable ride that still looks great on the road! It's got plenty of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
